-- MOVES-Tristan Thomas named director of portfolio strategy at Northern Trust Alternatives
-- 
-- Wed Aug 20, 2014 02:36PM EDT
-- None



Aug 20 (Reuters) - Northern Trust Corp's <NTRS.O> hedge fund group, Northern Trust Alternatives, has appointed Tristan Thomas as director of portfolio strategy.

Thomas will be responsible for portfolio construction and monitoring funds-of-funds and custom programs. He is also a member of the team's senior investment committee.